reviewText: Please don't just repackage old episodes under a different name--very deceiving and disappointing.
It is different from earlier videos. Interesting topic about bugs.
GREAT TAPE!  GRANDTWINS LOVE BARNEY!  JUST LIKE THEIR MOMMY DID!
Purchased this DVD to add to my daughter's collection. She brings a portable DVD player with her on the school bus and in our personal vehicle. She enjoyed watching it.
My grandson loves Barney and has enjoyed all the tapes we have ordered.
Not much to say. My daughter loves Barney!!
